  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Starship</span>, with a generous inventory capacity, and a balanced loadout of weaponry to allow for a variety of defence tactics.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Claim</span> this ship to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current ship. While on a planet, summon ships from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船</span>，配备大量的库存空间以及能适应各类防御战术的平衡性武器配备。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收取</span>这艘飞船，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的飞船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在行星上可以通过快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）召唤飞船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一艘特殊<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船</span>，擁有龐大道具欄容量和配置均衡的武器組合，可實行各種防禦策略。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">領取</span>這艘船加入你的收藏，或是與目前太空船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>皆可。在星球上時，可利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 召喚太空船。"
  },
